{"tid":2444789,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Tesla股東控告Elon Musk於Twitter胡言亂語影響股價","createTime":"2021-03-13T06:04:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T08:45:28.000Z","uid":28765,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a67a8d386246a9c21fda8b4492f5fb241a0ba5be","tid":2444789,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T06:04:36.000Z","msg":"《路透社》報導，特斯拉（TESLA）執行長馬斯克（Elon Musk）被股東以違反2018年與美國證管會（SEC）之間的和解協議為由告上法院，對此特斯拉及SEC並未立即回覆評論。<br />\n<br />\n根據周四公開的控告內容，除了馬斯克以外，該名股東也將特斯拉董事會列為被告。該名原告指控馬斯克「稀奇古怪（erratic）」的推文，以及特斯拉高層未確保馬斯克遵守與SEC之間和解協議，已使股東曝險於數十萬美元的虧損之中。<br />\n<br />\n根據控告內容，原告點名馬斯克過去在推特上的多則推文，包括去年5月他在推特上聲稱特斯拉股價「太高」，該則推文一出後，導致特斯拉市值崩跌超過130億美元。<br />\n<br />\n原告Chase Gharrity表示，馬斯克的舉動以及高層的不作為，已導致「實質的財務損害」，因此他們該賠償因為違反受託責任的損害。對此德拉瓦大學（University of Delaware）教授Charles Elson表示：「這可能導致SEC採取一些行動。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20210313/ZAG7BXOTUZB2VB7SMOIPC4YAOE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20210313%2FZAG7BXOTUZB2VB7SMOIPC4YAOE%2F&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXI2DcYOQIx6XO0JIcXsozN2c%3D&h=c30fa7a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20210313%2FZAG7BXOTUZB2VB7SMOIPC4YAOE%2F&h=826c82ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20210313/ZAG7BXOTUZB2VB7SMOIPC4YAOE/</a>"},{"pid":"ab07a074763cf07407bc14df93369676d5c8f762","tid":2444789,"uid":40250,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T06:24:06.000Z","msg":"On9 jai, tesla無左elon musk仲值呢個價？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"058ed198895a5c3760766f32d7de1cab448e8ae7","tid":2444789,"uid":350455,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ab07a074763cf07407bc14df93369676d5c8f762","tid":2444789,"uid":40250,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T06:24:06.000Z","msg":"On9 jai, tesla無左elon musk仲值呢個價？<img src=\"/assets/faces/no